  "detailed_description": "Welcome to picoSYNTH! A toy modular synth kit giving you a playful way to create simple loops and beats. By combining the equipment in interesting ways you can do anything from bleeps and bloops to crazy complex stuff. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949300/extras/8f9b26d6bb5324c680aa761abc5e82b8.poster.avif?t=1748894892\" width=384 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949300/extras/8f9b26d6bb5324c680aa761abc5e82b8.webm?t=1748894892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949300/extras/8f9b26d6bb5324c680aa761abc5e82b8.mp4?t=1748894892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Build rigs in playful and straightforward ways<br></li><li>Make beats and loops<br></li><li>Live tune while building your beat<br></li><li>Choose from multiple waveforms and equipment <br></li><li>Wire up your creations for unexpected results<br></li><li>Save files in easy to read text format<br></li><li>Export to WAV and import anywhere</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949300/extras/3d28c4fe07410866a39d0eccb4803981.apng?t=1748894892\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949300/extras/3d28c4fe07410866a39d0eccb4803981.poster.avif?t=1748894892\" class=\"bb_img\" width=384 height=384 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Quickstart</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use the [+] menu to create add equipment to the scene<br></li><li>Drag and drop things on the trashcan to delete it<br></li><li>Use cables to connect different equipment<br></li><li>You cannot have more than 4 speakers, use them wisely<br></li><li>Read the manual and experiment!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949300/extras/5f8e06375cb7015b932abbf73ee5bfd1.poster.avif?t=1748894892\" width=384 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949300/extras/5f8e06375cb7015b932abbf73ee5bfd1.webm?t=1748894892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949300/extras/5f8e06375cb7015b932abbf73ee5bfd1.mp4?t=1748894892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Welcome to picoSYNTH! A toy modular synth kit giving you a playful way to create simple loops and beats. By combining the equipment in interesting ways you can do anything from bleeps and bloops to crazy complex stuff. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949300/extras/8f9b26d6bb5324c680aa761abc5e82b8.poster.avif?t=1748894892\" width=384 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949300/extras/8f9b26d6bb5324c680aa761abc5e82b8.webm?t=1748894892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949300/extras/8f9b26d6bb5324c680aa761abc5e82b8.mp4?t=1748894892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Build rigs in playful and straightforward ways<br></li><li>Make beats and loops<br></li><li>Live tune while building your beat<br></li><li>Choose from multiple waveforms and equipment <br></li><li>Wire up your creations for unexpected results<br></li><li>Save files in easy to read text format<br></li><li>Export to WAV and import anywhere</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949300/extras/3d28c4fe07410866a39d0eccb4803981.apng?t=1748894892\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949300/extras/3d28c4fe07410866a39d0eccb4803981.poster.avif?t=1748894892\" class=\"bb_img\" width=384 height=384 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Quickstart</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use the [+] menu to create add equipment to the scene<br></li><li>Drag and drop things on the trashcan to delete it<br></li><li>Use cables to connect different equipment<br></li><li>You cannot have more than 4 speakers, use them wisely<br></li><li>Read the manual and experiment!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949300/extras/5f8e06375cb7015b932abbf73ee5bfd1.poster.avif?t=1748894892\" width=384 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949300/extras/5f8e06375cb7015b932abbf73ee5bfd1.webm?t=1748894892\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949300/extras/5f8e06375cb7015b932abbf73ee5bfd1.mp4?t=1748894892\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
